Sanlam Plans to Invest in Tanzania, Zambia This Year, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-06T04:58:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/sanlam-plans-to-invest-in-tanzania-zambia-this-year-business-day-reports.html
Sanlam Ltd. (SLM)  plans to invest in
medical insurance businesses in Tanzania and Zambia this year as
part of its growth strategy, Business Day reported.  The insurer is also considering opportunities elsewhere in
 Africa , the U.K. and  India , the Johannesburg-based newspaper
said, citing Chief Executive Officer Johan van Zyl.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  